comments: Dedmon (SAC) makes some body contact with Bogdanovic (UTA) as he attempts to gain post position, but does not affect Bogdanovic's ability to defend the play.
Gobert (UTA) legally contests Bogdanovic's (SAC) jump shot attempt.
Gobert (UTA) establishes himself in a screening position in Ariza's (SAC) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Ariza (SAC) slides his arms off of Gobert's (UTA) upper body without affecting Gobert's FOM as he attempts to get around the pick.
Bogdanovic (UTA) makes marginal contact with Fox (SAC) during his driving shot attempt.
Fox (SAC) makes marginal contact with his off-arm to Bogdanovic (UTA) during the driving shot attempt.
Bogdanovic (UTA) receives the pass and takes more than two steps after he has gathered the ball.
Mitchell (UTA) makes marginal contact with his left hand to Ariza's (SAC) arm as Ariza is naturally retreating toward the lane.
Gobert (UTA) establishes himself in a screening position in Ariza's (SAC) path and does not deliver the contact.
Dedmon (SAC) makes marginal contact with Gobert (UTA) that does not affect his ability to maintain control of the ball or finish at the rim.
Dedmon (SAC) establishes himself in a screening position and gives Mitchell (UTA) room to avoid the contact.
Bogdanovic (UTA) makes marginal contact with Fox (SAC) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Joseph (SAC) briefly has his hands around Ingles' (UTA) midsection, but releases without affecting his FOM.
Mitchell (UTA) disengages from the contact with Ariza (SAC) and the contact is marginal.
Ariza (SAC) makes marginal body contact with Mitchell (UTA) at the start of the drive.
Holmes (SAC) maintains verticality and absorbs the body contact made with Mitchell (UTA) during the driving shot attempt.
Gobert (UTA) extends his arms into Ariza (SAC) and dislodges him from his rebounding position.
Mitchell (UTA) makes marginal body contact with Fox (SAC) that does not affect his ability to pass.
Barnes (SAC) briefly has his arm around Mitchell's (UTA) back, but he slides it off without affecting Mitchell's FOM.
Ariza (SAC) engages with Bogdanovic (UTA) as the two go over the screen, but disengages without affecting Bogdanovic's FOM.
Gobert (UTA) establishes himself in a screening position in Ariza's (SAC) path and does not deliver the contact.
Holmes (SAC) makes marginal contact with Mitchell (UTA) that does not affect his SQBR.
Barnes (SAC) makes marginal contact with Gobert's (UTA) midsection that does not affect his ability to roll toward the basket.
